{"tid":259042,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"天王寺動物園","createTime":"2017-05-26T15:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T03:16:17.000Z","uid":14026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b40f77e1956c5939ae3aecbeb42eb04a57034a6e","tid":259042,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:01:42.000Z","msg":"最近呢一兩年有冇巴打去過天王寺動物園？<br />\n有冇人行入去覺得啲動物好似呆呆滯滯<br />\n全部都唔夠飽等死咁樣？<br />\n如果想反映又可以點？<br />\n仲有個問題係佢地連企鵝都夠膽放出黎比佢地暴曬⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b615609f376d62054d6379fd7de9deb59c9697","tid":259042,"uid":10062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:47:13.000Z","msg":"啲熊喺到自轉"},{"pid":"882cf628fde3f90ad794d5708db67ee57627ac67","tid":259042,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T22:18:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"051764ba1b3aad790827be7781ace8a69c2177d8","tid":259042,"uid":66557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T22:23:18.000Z","msg":"最生猛係隻老虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4977ad960832057c82e8fe9acb3a2333ced60bda","tid":259042,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:41:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fb66a99be1dd2685f859689b1cba355d5f7bbbe","tid":259042,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:55:13.000Z","msg":"去睇時 好多動物好似有精神病<br />\n不停籠中來回行<br />\n而且好瘦 好無精神<br />\n<br />\n仲有 長頸鹿 以我所知係食樹葉<br />\n但去睇時 見到佢食緊樹皮<br />\n睇真D 原來周圍係有好多樹葉<br />\n但好多都係矮灌木 或者係圍欄外<br />\n佢應該食唔到<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢度 我真係覺得班動物好可憐"},{"pid":"4cb236925c143b2c69be256a39badcceec7a2034","tid":259042,"uid":13724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:07:05.000Z","msg":"你借啲意想去動物園前行吓嗟，扮咩講動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a261fc3010e8272f0c0df765a04ac46a6571f6c","tid":259042,"uid":82915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:08:37.000Z","msg":"自從去過小諸動物園之後, 以後都唔去動物園"},{"pid":"4fbb4b1f635aeaaeefbd7a9f90cb89802e8e188b","tid":259042,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:17:17.000Z","msg":"仲有啲紅鶴企係度輪住嘔"},{"pid":"14bb143b79aa6d160d1d5612b2c5939e20bbd9b9","tid":259042,"uid":14347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:40:49.000Z","msg":"記得有度有好多丁滿，隻隻都係間劏房入面尖叫，行個陣好似玩outlast咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e1df7877a7840817aaceddbcbd41dd55ee3798","tid":259042,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:44:50.000Z","msg":"呢個動物園唔係人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef6be6cd59cea06261246fb762c8d47e547260c","tid":259042,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:45:32.000Z","msg":"隻北極熊同獅子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a83c2209132a3b36dcac2b2751a68d02d55d3bd","tid":259042,"uid":7637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:47:18.000Z","msg":"D企鵝甩毛"},{"pid":"5fbee8a389c8e52d15e6b8107b8b5c111872b939","tid":259042,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:47:26.000Z","msg":":<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96963dfa601f405a292eb89378f42d563eed2d65","tid":259042,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:47:35.000Z","msg":"夏天睇見隻北極熊...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1700fce962329302b77a9e052c222336057c414a","tid":259042,"uid":15404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:50:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你借啲意想去動物園前行吓嗟，扮咩講動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973692dfad791abb379068f9567330f7fdeaef5c","tid":259042,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:52:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得有度有好多丁滿，隻隻都係間劏房入面尖叫，行個陣好似玩outlast咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每隻野都風燭殘年咁"},{"pid":"3a518170790b30430ba7521f3d648cc93528f73b","tid":259042,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:54:58.000Z","msg":"動物園呢樣產物本身就唔人道<br />\n幾時先取締到呢樣野"},{"pid":"d898a67b5c27d9b9b12eeaab04ca26ba59acd5e3","tid":259042,"uid":32391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:56:14.000Z","msg":"上次冬天去果時 見到d猩猩凍到縮埋一舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f70e9388887028df1c014515ff860b8bfaa432","tid":259042,"uid":119022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:58:14.000Z","msg":"行完成身痕。<br />\n仲有d鹿不斷不斷用鹿角撞鐵閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cbb1f0c3457a43e5707d9cd267c264621238de","tid":259042,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T02:55:32.000Z","msg":"北極熊個身係綠色，生哂菁苔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20feb2cad969ac1772ab56a34661b8c06777c4aa","tid":259042,"uid":69698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:12:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170527&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=56747510\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170527%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D56747510&d=bUBsLvHP2HZHpr%2F2v29sAY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=4a3ff578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170527%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D56747510&h=b8a15d62\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170527&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=56747510</a>"},{"pid":"4aa3aec2f83d3d363075ef06501f05495a01560b","tid":259042,"uid":116796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:13:39.000Z","msg":"幾年前去過 個環境/配套比想像中好殘舊<br />\nD動物無黎精神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印象最深刻係現場睇烏龜交配<br />\n叫得勁大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3d08faab538e61cfbb9edc137702465483cfb8","tid":259042,"uid":21455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:18:43.000Z","msg":"唯有唔去,等佢執"},{"pid":"be7cb996f3458a79b4ea2ea9fea500a873cf122c","tid":259042,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:21:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你借啲意想去動物園前行吓嗟，扮咩講動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飛田新地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add8ee4ebeb62dbad8aeed6637a38466ad1c9083","tid":259042,"uid":94182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜先去完<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/113010_212239aa49aebe60c146dcf350f76ff7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F113010_212239aa49aebe60c146dcf350f76ff7.jpg&h=79586852&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/113027_4f9f7033378ce7d876431b81f568aef1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F113027_4f9f7033378ce7d876431b81f568aef1.jpg&h=26d9636a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/113028_f046f8ca53da5d45f6b4a848d9031e1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F113028_f046f8ca53da5d45f6b4a848d9031e1d.jpg&h=cbc513c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/113028_fc7ab7cbbc01d8ed8397aa6fc308d8cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F113028_fc7ab7cbbc01d8ed8397aa6fc308d8cb.jpg&h=2bfb7a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到隻北極熊係咁自轉 心諗做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e977ddeeb11c309d8cc7e78d39a85eec10e212e","tid":259042,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:42:46.000Z","msg":"其實唔止呢個動物園，好多都係咁<br />\n會有唔少動物係到不斷重複做同一個動作，例如自轉，抬腿<br />\n上網搵過，好似話係因為環境令佢地唔自在，放鬆唔到先會咁做<br />\n所以我去過動物園見到咁之後都發誓唔會再去了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0812981d5a5809b8a5a57b710322a4c46a27f2ee","tid":259042,"uid":2676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:46:23.000Z","msg":"旭川動物園果兩隻北極熊 我以為睇緊機械人，同一條路線+同一個抬頭動作loop唔停"},{"pid":"3ce8650812f2bc20d0620b56a3685673e5bd08f6","tid":259042,"uid":94182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>旭川動物園果兩隻北極熊 我以為睇緊機械人，同一條路線+同一個抬頭動作loop唔停</blockquote><br />\n我以為係表演緊或自娛緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d69967bc87d41a4fb3d0cc9cbb1d6526ecda391","tid":259042,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>旭川動物園果兩隻北極熊 我以為睇緊機械人，同一條路線+同一個抬頭動作loop唔停</blockquote><br />\n我以為係表演緊或自娛緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能佢慣左去某個地方抬頭就有野食"},{"pid":"822382853ec9a03c56d1a40b95c1dd60394bd620","tid":259042,"uid":101823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"之前去上野個動物員都係咁"},{"pid":"11fbf491f39a15f45fcbd7715bcfcea0e278e75f","tid":259042,"uid":99004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:19:53.000Z","msg":"天王寺動物園 我只係諗到飛田新地"},{"pid":"5eab81a4b6d745befea5c61764c28506110e5f15","tid":259042,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:21:33.000Z","msg":"100年前動物園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係太舊"},{"pid":"90b8fc3c6e9726b6b4e129f8005235b16730144f","tid":259042,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:21:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天王寺動物園 我只係諗到飛田新地</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb4a046772211bd83247d8139ffa668acb8348b","tid":259042,"uid":22069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻北極熊好黃<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/122343_cbf5e254dd08ec0c5628fc5895bc5c24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F122343_cbf5e254dd08ec0c5628fc5895bc5c24.jpg&h=93111aac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"714efe3f44a24377feaaef9622a5339840058b15","tid":259042,"uid":24641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:44:26.000Z","msg":"絕命精神病動物園"},{"pid":"ddd3983781a54603e91f2615a4c14b4038c0310b","tid":259042,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:49:07.000Z","msg":"卍阿彌陀佛卍"},{"pid":"2626914fa861ad4bf5ae0295fd81145e8a92fedd","tid":259042,"uid":75578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:50:16.000Z","msg":"間野真係睇完 會唔開心既動物園...<br />\n<br />\n好鬼細.... 大笨象對住個牆發呆...<br />\nD熊全部都精神病係度來回走坐成日（同一路線）<br />\n得返老虎有少少神氣...."},{"pid":"926db33b0c368511f1647d2d62cf49cf8203e1b0","tid":259042,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:37:11.000Z","msg":"呢啲舊式動物園其實同監獄無分別<br />\n<br />\n講真搵個19籠困鳩你幾年，食餐飯都俾人望住晒，你都想發癲啦<br />\n<br />\n就算佢整到青山綠水都好，都同真嗰個冇得揮<br />\n<br />\n呢個動物園聽人講喺tripadvisor嗰度就俾鬼佬插到飛天，所以我都唔敢去"},{"pid":"29cec212184ca4019ed974df6af1cab31b86dd55","tid":259042,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲舊式動物園其實同監獄無分別<br />\n<br />\n講真搵個19籠困鳩你幾年，食餐飯都俾人望住晒，你都想發癲啦<br />\n<br />\n就算佢整到青山綠水都好，都同真嗰個冇得揮<br />\n<br />\n呢個動物園聽人講喺tripadvisor嗰度就俾鬼佬插到飛天，所以我都唔敢去</blockquote><br />\n有冇得出email屌下？<br />\n我日文都尚算講到既"},{"pid":"e61fe6576798de8ba1b9a22745614d8ff430b9da","tid":259042,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:44:12.000Z","msg":"去阿笨阿占個動物園<br />\nD熊直頭好似住集中營咁<br />\n幾廿隻一齊住<br />\n<br />\n不過可能都好過孤伶伶一隻住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979522c7c7f1f3cd83fe3115ae4bdfb4ca80c163","tid":259042,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T06:55:43.000Z","msg":"原來都唔係近年既事"},{"pid":"2b8ac22d7a95f0664d815e6321f5a2888e12540b","tid":259042,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T07:04:56.000Z","msg":"見到隻北極熊真係最撚心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個園得啲雀仔係開心<br />\n仲有啲係外來鳥係個網上面築巢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483f15903fb9